snippet: The interim prime minister, Arseniy P. Yatsenyuk, sought to rally support for a Security Council resolution criticizing the Russian moves on Crimea.
abstract: Ukraine’s interim Prime Min Arseniy P Yatsenyuk, seeking to rally support for United Nations Security Council resolution criticizing Russian takeover of Crimea, makes plea for peaceful resolution to crisis.
lead_paragraph: The interim prime minister, Arseniy P. Yatsenyuk, sought to rally support for a Security Council resolution criticizing the Russian moves on Crimea.

headline.main: Ukraine Premier Makes Plea at the U.N.
headline.print_headline: Premier of Ukraine Makes Plea at the U.N.
